  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But still, not everything, you know, really came to a conclusion for sure, is that they are going to use the police that were pro-German a lot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they will use-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will try the-- the-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The context with that they have the pro-Nazis, a lot there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they have themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They after their father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew that already, whatever will happen, somebody's looking after him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was our fear also when the El Al came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They weren't coming to the conclusion that El Al came for some-- something other, other thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So all this was taken into consideration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why he was disguised, that even they see him, they wouldn't know that he's the guy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the reason for disguising him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even the disguise also was a-- it wouldn't-- let's say it was-- it wouldn't work like that we can bring him into the airport.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After bringing somewhere else, we are no going to leave him like this, again start the story.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, that was the reason that-- that-- how do you say?-- that the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what was the-- Well, just about the sons who-- who-- who--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, that the-- that was really the disguise and the guard of him, because we had been afraid that the family would be there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what happened, really, that-- I don't remember exactly the timing, but they came later.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they looked after him, but the airplane already left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they came--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I think so, that they came-- I-- I'm not sure on a half hour or this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I know they came later, and it was too late.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they came when the airplane already left.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
